  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effect of teledermatology on length of hospital admission, length of stay, 30 day
      readmission rate, and antibiotic use in patients presenting with cellulitis vs
      pseudocellulitis in an academic emergency department setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
